Class PostfixExpression

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.sanity4j.util.math.PostfixExpression

public class PostfixExpression
extends Object

PostFixExpression - evaluates postfix expressions like [1, 2, +]. Variables can be used, prefix them with a '#'.

Version:
1.0 02/01/2008
Author:
Yiannis Paschalidis
